Benjamin W. Wise et al., Appellees, v. Potomac National Bank of Potomac, Illinois et al., Appellants.Gen. No. 9,473.

Cause transferred.

Heard in this court at the October term, 1945;opinion filed October 23, 1945;released for publication November 19, 1945.Steely, Steely, Graham & Dysert and Hutton, Clark & Hutton, for appellants; H. Ernest Hutton and Benjamin I. Norwood, Jr., of counsel; Rearick & Rearick for appellees.

Opinion by

Presiding Justice Hayes.

Not to be published in full.
